longBusinessSummary: Inca One Gold Corp. operates as a Canadian-based mineral resource and mineral processing company with gold milling facilities in Peru. It develops and operates Chala One and Kori One gold-bearing mineral processing facilities. The company was formerly known as Inca One Resources Corp. and changed its name to Inca One Gold Corp. in September 2014. Inca One Gold Corp. was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
